---
const supportServer = "https://discord.gg/RdwtR7HQbr";
const githubRepo = "https://github.com/Dragon-Bot-CoC/Dragon-Bot-2.0/issues";
---

<section id="support" class="py-24 bg-slate-950 px-6">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white mb-6">
          Need a <span class="text-orange-500">Hand?</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-slate-400 text-lg mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          Whether you've found a bug in the <strong>9-minute heartbeat</strong> logic or you just need help configuring <strong>/receiveposts</strong>, our community is ready to help.
        </p>

        <div class="space-y-6">
          <a href={supportServer}
           target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
           class="flex items-center gap-4 p-6 bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-2xl hover:border-indigo-500 transition-all group">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-indigo-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-2xl shadow-lg shadow-indigo-500/20">
              💬
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="text-white font-bold">Join the Support Server</h4>
              <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">Real-time help from the Dragon Bot team.</p>
            </div>
          </a>

          <a href={githubRepo} 
           target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
           class="flex items-center gap-4 p-6 bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-2xl hover:border-orange-500 transition-all group">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-slate-800 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-2xl">
              🐛
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="text-white font-bold">Report a Bug</h4>
              <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">Open an issue on GitHub for technical errors.</p>
            </div>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-slate-900/50 p-8 rounded-3xl border border-slate-800 backdrop-blur-sm">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Quick Fixes</h3>
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="border-b border-slate-800 pb-4">
            <h5 class="text-orange-400 font-bold text-sm mb-2 uppercase tracking-wide">Why is the bot offline?</h5>
            <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm">The bot uses a 9-minute heartbeat to stay awake on Railway. If it's down, we're likely pushing a new update!</p>
          </div>
          <div class="border-b border-slate-800 pb-4">
            <h5 class="text-orange-400 font-bold text-sm mb-2 uppercase tracking-wide">How do I start?</h5>
            <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm">Use <code>/setclantag</code> followed by your #tag to link your clan and activate war reminders.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h5 class="text-orange-400 font-bold text-sm mb-2 uppercase tracking-wide">Turn off Notifications?</h5>
            <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm">Admins can disable either or both war & raid notifications using /disable_reminders.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>